---
import PanelSingle from "../panel_single.astro";
import Button from "../blue_button.astro";
---

<PanelSingle style="bg-[#103364] text-neutral-200">
    <div class="my-4 text-3xl font-bold">Contributors Welcome!</div>

    <p>
        Surge XT is supported by a community of volunteer open source developers, designers,
        testers, musicians, synthesizer enthusiasts, and content creators.
    </p>

    <p>
        Without them, none of would have been possible. If you're interested in seeing what's going
        on with the project, the best thing to do is:
    </p>

    <Button text="View the Surge XT Repository" url="https://github.com/surge-synthesizer/surge" />
</PanelSingle>
